It would be great to be able to add a list to a page in Confluence that is both a numbered list and a task list with checkboxes to mark items completed.

Use Case: We have a page that we copy and edit for each deployment, which currently contains several numbered lists. We also want to add checkboxes to the lists so we can mark things completed, but if we do this we lost the numbers. Numbers are really handy to refer to steps and we make enough edits that we need the list to automatically adjust numbering.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-36762].
