Currently {{UserAccessor.getUserByName()}} uses Hibernate query cache, which can become slow to use with large Hibernate sessions. Putting this information in a separate cache should speed up this operation considerably.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This bug report is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding bug report|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-36748].
  {panel}

when I want to extract an image from the first page of pdf file, some pictures in the first page will be disappeared, when I open the image file

