The new image viewer is useful as a platform to discuss and get feedback from users about layouts and screen designs.

At the moment, there is no indicator of Zoom Level ( % ) when clicking the "Zoom In" and "Zoom Out" buttons/links.

It would be very useful to have this feature so that users are aware about the current size of the image they view.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
