Currently permission checking during search scales really badly on instances where users have a lot of groups and there are lot of page restrictions. There's a lot of room for improvement in the current algorithm.

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *Confluence Cloud*. Using *Confluence Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/CONFSERVER-36654].
