It would be very useful to have the capability to copy or move inline comments (for example in PDF files) to the latest version of the uploaded file.

For example, if I upload a new version of a PDF that changes things that are not strictly related to comments, I want to retain those comments and make them available only or even in the last version (move/copy).

In this case the PDF has exactly the same number of pages and sizes.

